"},{"pid":"4f9a2f0043f2bf89cf29f54e083c27f5b1adf238","tid":317061,"uid":71527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T08:58:29.000Z","msg":"今年真係好少學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n讀書都要揀時機出世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a97debac31b928ecf15a3ad3144cbd8c644249ce","tid":317061,"uid":4014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T09:01:03.000Z","msg":"唔好入civil 今年到而家仲有幾十人收唔到intern offer<br />\n<br />\n而家先入已經遲到仆街 畢業後冇哂野做真係仆街喊三聲"},{"pid":"464d2bb7c501acbb4be371837f665362f43df2b7","tid":317061,"uid":28614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T09:02:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好入civil 今年到而家仲有幾十人收唔到intern offer<br />\n<br />\n而家先入已經遲到仆街 畢業後冇哂野做真係仆街喊三聲</blockquote><br />\n紅磚 ME 都一大班 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c092f90e76d2af71f8405dd798c2b1e809fc3c1","tid":317061,"uid":71527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T09:02:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>利申：ME 仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔好揀錯科入我呢 d 夕陽工程科 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nME 2016 人工比 2015 跌左成千 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁又唔可以只睇頭一兩年人工嘅。。長遠ME grad 都有個明確路向發展。poly ME都好似好耐歷史啦。我以前都有諗過讀poly Mech 嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c83fcb316155626b3c8ea755546e82625d04c918","tid":317061,"uid":71527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T09:06:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好入civil 今年到而家仲有幾十人收唔到intern offer<br />\n<br />\n而家先入已經遲到仆街 畢業後冇哂野做真係仆街喊三聲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n今年的確係差左。<br />\n<br />\n不過揀科唔好睇咁短，換轉講四年後嘅事又邊個知？四年前班友入civil 都唔知會咁啦。你畢業後做野都只少做30年啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋civil 差，其他建造相關工程都唔會好&hellip;"},{"pid":"81c62fe1769993d9e864d9b3bdc8d730ece3e1eb","tid":317061,"uid":71527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T09:07:31.000Z","msg":"讀engine真係幾辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ccbc5d0c3e1109c2ae09eafe02a1033e1f73a6a","tid":317061,"uid":66291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T09:20:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>To learn and to apply<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nFor the benefit of mankind <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b46e63dc28431d49f119e445d028bfc47b2c842f","tid":317061,"uid":14092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T09:32:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>利申：ME 仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔好揀錯科入我呢 d 夕陽工程科 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nME 2016 人工比 2015 跌左成千 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁又唔可以只睇頭一兩年人工嘅。。長遠ME grad 都有個明確路向發展。poly ME都好似好耐歷史啦。我以前都有諗過讀poly Mech 嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁巴打你家陣讀緊咩<br />\n黎緊讀poly me<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d1e3d95cd093c10cc7d43f22ebef6f9ed76b58c","tid":317061,"uid":98022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T09:37:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>各位 DSE 分數應該唔差 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有幾科推薦有與趣入工程既同學仔揀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/11/154437_b049b8083591e8a51ff7f39ff8636a61.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservi